# Author: Amy B.
#

PURPOSE
---------------------------
    Play a number guessing game with user. User able to 
    guess (with hints) until correct number is guessed.

ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS
---------------------------
    Python exercise taken from:
        Automate the Boring Stuff with Python
        By Al Sweigart

FILES
---------------------------
    - README:       this file
    - guess.py:     main program driver.

RUN
---------------------------
    Run with:
        python guess.py

    - or with a batch file:

        guess

BUGS/Notes
---------------------------
    Does not handle when user enters invalid input.